{
  "stem": "1929.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I remember I was standing, almost next to them, and the blood running on the ground, and all the brains coming out from their head.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ones I remember was adults.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then most of the-- then the Germans would tried all kinds of tricks to get the people out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said like, for example, we'll let you come out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'll make you legal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, when they came out, they wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took them to the great synagogue and interned them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like 500 people at a time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have vague memories of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I know that my sister, Lola, was-- was-- was caught.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was in one of those-- in that synagogue, or just before she got to a synagogue, some other place, she was able to escape.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were terrible things going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Like parents used to come to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they would walk up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They'd said, we'll trade places with our children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Take us.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Or they would give them money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And sometimes, some people did buy themselves out from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But anyhow, you know, I didn't see that obviously.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But from a historical point of view, the older people-- also there was terrible atrocities by the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They would amuse themselves by taking babies and frying them in hot water and over fire and splitting their heads and shooting into the place.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean there was just-- there was no limits, no limits whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But anyhow, the-- most of the people that were found hiding were eventually moved into the forest, outside of the town, very close.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They had to march there, dig their own graves, and they were all shot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it's all documented.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe so.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have a book.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
